00:34:47,625 --> 00:34:50,416
Kita bahas setelah Ibu pulang nanti malam.

473
00:34:54,208 --> 00:34:55,041
Hei.

474
00:34:56,916 --> 00:34:57,833
Semua akan berlalu.

475
00:35:07,458 --> 00:35:10,125
